{"tid":2012170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係忍你唔到， A Sir 炒樓又食女","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T08:44:06.000Z","uid":146880,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2b3f99f4a5ea0ca4890dbe7d41fcd24e3e9abbbd","tid":2012170,"uid":146880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，今日有件事要同大家爆料。<br />\n我猶疑左好耐，都係決定講出黎。<br />\n我大家姐Macy(化名)，好耐之前比一條自稱樓神的神棍食過。<br />\n佢係做生意的，個名叫AnXXXXXy Sir，佢好似係搞埋D呃人買大陸樓投資果D，平時就係網上寫溝女天書，樓市專題。<br />\n我家姐Macy以前係酒吧識左佢，佢果樣木木毒毒成個公公咁，成日話自己炒樓賺過幾千萬，係咁訊信攻勢追人，結果激情難抗比佢上左。<br />\n點知唔夠 3 個月就拋棄左我家姐，受好大傷害，成7年冇拍拖。<br />\n今時今日撞翻妮條神棍，聽聞佢炒西環樓發左達，仲買佐好多大陸樓，身邊大把女埋身，仲成日約埋D臭雞人妻玩NTR 旅行。<br />\n大家認住妮個人，唔好受佢欺騙！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXQHu4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXQHu4i.png&h=0d34bcde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/anthony.chung.is\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fanthony.chung.is&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97Hcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0754e62e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/anthony.chung.is</a><br />\n佢FB<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5p1LDX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5p1LDX.jpg&h=3ea570b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Umm7Gce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmm7Gce.jpg&h=89e69716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efvgzxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fefvgzxr.jpg&h=052b15c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys9dBLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys9dBLM.jpg&h=6f45f10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esj895Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fesj895Q.jpg&h=63feb4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br